title: Increase deployment job timeout [!pr]
body:
#### Purpose
- [ ] Feature
- [ ] Bug Fix
- [x] Other

#### Associated Tickets
No ticket

#### Details
CircleCI will terminate jobs that have had no output for more than 10 minutes. Our migrations will sometimes take longer than that, so I'm extending the timeout to 4h50m, which is 10m less than the max job time (5h).

#### Checklist
- [ ] Documentation
- [ ] Tests

title: Increase migration job timeouts
body:
#### Purpose
- [ ] Feature
- [ ] Bug Fix
- [ ] Other

#### Associated Tickets
No ticket

#### Details
We were allowing the migration job to run for 10 minutes, but lately we've introduced migrations that take longer.
CircleCI has a limit of 5 hours per job, so here I'm setting the migration job timeout to 4h50m to make sure we finish before that.

#### Checklist
- [ ] Documentation
- [ ] Tests
